{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":944,"text":"I want to talk a little bit today\nabout labor and work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":6500,"text":"When we think about how people work,"},{"time":9246,"text":"the naive intuition we have"},{"time":11639,"text":"is that people are like rats in a maze --"},{"time":14027,"text":"that all people care about is money,"},{"time":16020,"text":"and the moment we give them money,"},{"time":17696,"text":"we can direct them to work one way,"},{"time":19418,"text":"we can direct them to work another way."},{"time":21422,"text":"This is why we give bonuses to bankers\nand pay in all kinds of ways."},{"time":25057,"text":"And we really have\nthis incredibly simplistic view"},{"time":28549,"text":"of why people work, and what\nthe labor market looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32843,"text":"At the same time, if you think about it,"},{"time":35190,"text":"there's all kinds of strange behaviors\nin the world around us."},{"time":38910,"text":"Think about something like mountaineering\nand mountain climbing."},{"time":42275,"text":"If you read books of people\nwho climb mountains, difficult mountains,"},{"time":46550,"text":"do you think that those books are full\nof moments of joy and happiness?"},{"time":51699,"text":"No, they are full of misery."},{"time":54040,"text":"In fact, it's all about frostbite\nand having difficulty walking,"},{"time":57722,"text":"and difficulty breathing --"},{"time":59406,"text":"cold, challenging circumstances."},{"time":62468,"text":"And if people were just trying\nto be happy,"},{"time":64946,"text":"the moment they would get to the top,"},{"time":66827,"text":"they would say,\n\"This was a terrible mistake."},{"time":68976,"text":"I'll never do it again.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":70381,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71522,"text":"\"Instead, let me sit on a beach\nsomewhere drinking mojitos.\""},{"time":75161,"text":"But instead, people go down,"},{"time":78859,"text":"and after they recover, they go up again."},{"time":81756,"text":"And if you think about\nmountain climbing as an example,"},{"time":84850,"text":"it suggests all kinds of things."},{"time":87206,"text":"It suggests that we care\nabout reaching the end, a peak."},{"time":91135,"text":"It suggests that we care\nabout the fight, about the challenge."},{"time":94666,"text":"It suggests that there's all kinds\nof other things that motivate us"},{"time":98150,"text":"to work or behave in all kinds of ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102322,"text":"And for me personally,\nI started thinking about this"},{"time":104821,"text":"after a student came to visit me."},{"time":108085,"text":"This was one of my students\nfrom a few years earlier,"},{"time":112014,"text":"and he came one day back to campus."},{"time":114204,"text":"And he told me the following story:"},{"time":116359,"text":"He said that for more than two weeks,"},{"time":118805,"text":"he was working\non a PowerPoint presentation."},{"time":121850,"text":"He was working in a big bank,"},{"time":123620,"text":"and this was in preparation\nfor a merger and acquisition."},{"time":127430,"text":"And he was working very hard\non this presentation --"},{"time":129945,"text":"graphs, tables, information."},{"time":131954,"text":"He stayed late at night every day."},{"time":135464,"text":"And the day before it was due,"},{"time":137678,"text":"he sent his PowerPoint\npresentation to his boss,"},{"time":141012,"text":"and his boss wrote him back and said,"},{"time":143642,"text":"\"Nice presentation,\nbut the merger is canceled.\""},{"time":148340,"text":"And the guy was deeply depressed."},{"time":150475,"text":"Now at the moment when he was working,"},{"time":152659,"text":"he was actually quite happy."},{"time":154543,"text":"Every night he was enjoying his work,"},{"time":156822,"text":"he was staying late, he was perfecting\nthis PowerPoint presentation."},{"time":161520,"text":"But knowing that nobody would ever\nwatch it made him quite depressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166779,"text":"So I started thinking\nabout how do we experiment"},{"time":169327,"text":"with this idea of the fruits of our labor."},{"time":173366,"text":"And to start with, we created\na little experiment"},{"time":177588,"text":"in which we gave people Legos,"},{"time":180618,"text":"and we asked them to build with Legos."},{"time":183960,"text":"And for some people,\nwe gave them Legos and we said,"},{"time":187501,"text":"\"Hey, would you like to build\nthis Bionicle for three dollars?"},{"time":192270,"text":"We'll pay you three dollars for it.\""},{"time":194344,"text":"And people said yes,\nand they built with these Legos."},{"time":197872,"text":"And when they finished, we took it,\nwe put it under the table,"},{"time":201462,"text":"and we said, \"Would you like\nto build another one,"},{"time":204471,"text":"this time for $2.70?\""},{"time":206471,"text":"If they said yes,\nwe gave them another one,"},{"time":208512,"text":"and when they finished, we asked them,"},{"time":210393,"text":"\"Do you want to build another one?\"\nfor $2.40, $2.10, and so on,"},{"time":214237,"text":"until at some point people said,"},{"time":216111,"text":"\"No more. It's not worth it for me.\""},{"time":220102,"text":"This was what we called\nthe meaningful condition."},{"time":222778,"text":"People built one Bionicle after another."},{"time":225829,"text":"After they finished every one of them,"},{"time":227679,"text":"we put them under the table."},{"time":229048,"text":"And we told them that at the end\nof the experiment,"},{"time":231456,"text":"we will take all these Bionicles,\nwe will disassemble them,"},{"time":234556,"text":"we will put them back in the boxes,"},{"time":236403,"text":"and we will use it\nfor the next participant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239727,"text":"There was another condition."},{"time":241282,"text":"This other condition was inspired\nby David, my student."},{"time":245814,"text":"And this other condition we called\nthe Sisyphic condition."},{"time":249266,"text":"And if you remember\nthe story about Sisyphus,"},{"time":251475,"text":"Sisyphus was punished by the gods\nto push the same rock up a hill,"},{"time":256726,"text":"and when he almost got to the end,"},{"time":258811,"text":"the rock would roll over,\nand he would have to start again."},{"time":261795,"text":"And you can think about this\nas the essence of doing futile work."},{"time":266691,"text":"You can imagine that if he pushed\nthe rock on different hills,"},{"time":269668,"text":"at least he would have\nsome sense of progress."},{"time":272316,"text":"Also, if you look at prison movies,"},{"time":275024,"text":"sometimes the way that the guards\ntorture the prisoners"},{"time":278207,"text":"is to get them to dig a hole,\nand when the prisoner is finished,"},{"time":281866,"text":"they ask him to fill the hole\nback up and then dig again."},{"time":284889,"text":"There's something\nabout this cyclical version"},{"time":287095,"text":"of doing something over and over and over"},{"time":289734,"text":"that seems to be\nparticularly demotivating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292575,"text":"So in the second condition\nof this experiment,"},{"time":294806,"text":"that's exactly what we did."},{"time":296496,"text":"We asked people,"},{"time":297807,"text":"\"Would you like to build\none Bionicle for three dollars?\""},{"time":300990,"text":"And if they said yes, they built it."},{"time":303309,"text":"Then we asked them, \"Do you want\nto build another one for $2.70?\""},{"time":306738,"text":"And if they said yes,\nwe gave them a new one,"},{"time":309906,"text":"and as they were building it,"},{"time":311715,"text":"we took apart the one\nthat they just finished."},{"time":315515,"text":"And when they finished that,"},{"time":317136,"text":"we said, \"Would you like\nto build another one,"},{"time":319332,"text":"this time for 30 cents less?\""},{"time":320878,"text":"And if they said yes,"},{"time":322101,"text":"we gave them the one\nthat they built and we broke."},{"time":325276,"text":"So this was an endless cycle\nof them building,"},{"time":328887,"text":"and us destroying in front of their eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332643,"text":"Now what happens when you compare\nthese two conditions?"},{"time":336343,"text":"The first thing that happened was\nthat people built many more Bionicles --"},{"time":339898,"text":"eleven in the meaningful condition,"},{"time":342160,"text":"versus seven in the Sisyphus condition."},{"time":344922,"text":"And by the way, we should point out\nthat this was not big meaning."},{"time":348059,"text":"People were not curing cancer\nor building bridges."},{"time":350620,"text":"People were building\nBionicles for a few cents."},{"time":354383,"text":"And not only that, everybody knew"},{"time":356360,"text":"that the Bionicles\nwould be destroyed quite soon."},{"time":359686,"text":"So there was not a real\nopportunity for big meaning."},{"time":362541,"text":"But even the small meaning\nmade a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366471,"text":"Now we had another version\nof this experiment."},{"time":368813,"text":"In this other version of the experiment,"},{"time":370752,"text":"we didn't put people in this situation,"},{"time":372719,"text":"we just described to them the situation,"},{"time":374749,"text":"much as I am describing to you now,"},{"time":376879,"text":"and we asked them to predict\nwhat the result would be."},{"time":380258,"text":"What happened?"},{"time":381441,"text":"People predicted the right direction\nbut not the right magnitude."},{"time":385491,"text":"People who were just given\nthe description of the experiment"},{"time":389198,"text":"said that in the meaningful condition,"},{"time":391110,"text":"people would probably build\none more Bionicle."},{"time":393792,"text":"So people understand\nthat meaning is important,"},{"time":396045,"text":"they just don't understand\nthe magnitude of the importance,"},{"time":398903,"text":"the extent to which it's important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401657,"text":"There was one other piece\nof data we looked at."},{"time":404474,"text":"If you think about it, there are\nsome people who love Legos,"},{"time":407355,"text":"and some people who don't."},{"time":408841,"text":"And you would speculate\nthat the people who love Legos"},{"time":411428,"text":"would build more Legos,\neven for less money,"},{"time":413544,"text":"because after all,\nthey get more internal joy from it."},{"time":416765,"text":"And the people who love Legos less\nwould build less Legos"},{"time":419885,"text":"because the enjoyment\nthat they derive from it is lower."},{"time":422813,"text":"And that's actually what we found\nin the meaningful condition."},{"time":425765,"text":"There was a very nice correlation\nbetween the love of Legos"},{"time":428598,"text":"and the amount of Legos people built."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431012,"text":"What happened in the Sisyphic condition?"},{"time":433679,"text":"In that condition,\nthe correlation was zero --"},{"time":436314,"text":"there was no relationship\nbetween the love of Legos,"},{"time":439059,"text":"and how much people built,"},{"time":440846,"text":"which suggests to me\nthat with this manipulation"},{"time":443545,"text":"of breaking things\nin front of people's eyes,"},{"time":446007,"text":"we basically crushed any joy\nthat they could get out of this activity."},{"time":450580,"text":"We basically eliminated it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453833,"text":"Soon after I finished\nrunning this experiment,"},{"time":457078,"text":"I went to talk to a big\nsoftware company in Seattle."},{"time":461392,"text":"I can't tell you who they were,\nbut they were a big company in Seattle."},{"time":465260,"text":"This was a group\nwithin the software company"},{"time":467372,"text":"that was put in a different building,"},{"time":469188,"text":"and they asked them to innovate,"},{"time":470832,"text":"and create the next big product\nfor this company."},{"time":474590,"text":"And the week before I showed up,"},{"time":476143,"text":"the CEO of this big software company\nwent to that group, 200 engineers,"},{"time":480574,"text":"and canceled the project."},{"time":483311,"text":"And I stood there in front of 200"},{"time":485365,"text":"of the most depressed\npeople I've ever talked to."},{"time":489014,"text":"And I described to them\nsome of these Lego experiments,"},{"time":491661,"text":"and they said they felt like they had\njust been through that experiment."},{"time":497053,"text":"And I asked them, I said,"},{"time":498300,"text":"\"How many of you now show up\nto work later than you used to?\""},{"time":501916,"text":"And everybody raised their hand."},{"time":503894,"text":"I said, \"How many of you now go home\nearlier than you used to?\""},{"time":507093,"text":"Everybody raised their hand."},{"time":509006,"text":"I asked them, \"How many of you now add"},{"time":511709,"text":"not-so-kosher things\nto your expense reports?\""},{"time":514866,"text":"And they didn't raise their hands,"},{"time":516541,"text":"but they took me out to dinner"},{"time":518010,"text":"and showed me what they could do\nwith expense reports."},{"time":522580,"text":"And then I asked them, I said,"},{"time":524056,"text":"\"What could the CEO have done\nto make you not as depressed?\""},{"time":528421,"text":"And they came up with all kinds of ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530548,"text":"They said the CEO could have asked\nthem to present to the whole company"},{"time":533953,"text":"about their journey\nover the last two years"},{"time":535980,"text":"and what they decided to do."},{"time":537406,"text":"He could have asked them to think\nabout which aspect of their technology"},{"time":541190,"text":"could fit with other parts\nof the organization."},{"time":544536,"text":"He could have asked them to build\nsome next-generation prototypes,"},{"time":547878,"text":"and see how they would work."},{"time":549903,"text":"But the thing is that any one of those\nwould require some effort and motivation."},{"time":554912,"text":"And I think the CEO basically did not\nunderstand the importance of meaning."},{"time":559116,"text":"If the CEO, just like our participants,"},{"time":561338,"text":"thought the essence\nof meaning is unimportant,"},{"time":564323,"text":"then he [wouldn't] care."},{"time":565561,"text":"And he would say, \"At the moment\nI directed you in this way,"},{"time":568484,"text":"and now that I'm directing\nyou in this way,"},{"time":570531,"text":"everything will be okay.\""},{"time":572077,"text":"But if you understood\nhow important meaning is,"},{"time":574776,"text":"then you would figure out\nthat it's actually important"},{"time":577378,"text":"to spend some time, energy and effort"},{"time":579196,"text":"in getting people to care more\nabout what they're doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583322,"text":"The next experiment\nwas slightly different."},{"time":585457,"text":"We took a sheet of paper\nwith random letters,"},{"time":588116,"text":"and we asked people\nto find pairs of letters"},{"time":590227,"text":"that were identical next to each other."},{"time":592282,"text":"That was the task."},{"time":593466,"text":"People did the first sheet,"},{"time":594894,"text":"then we asked if they wanted to do\nanother for a little less money,"},{"time":598263,"text":"the next sheet for a little bit\nless, and so on and so forth."},{"time":601163,"text":"And we had three conditions."},{"time":602747,"text":"In the first condition, people\nwrote their name on the sheet,"},{"time":606351,"text":"found all the pairs of letters,"},{"time":608665,"text":"gave it to the experimenter,"},{"time":610330,"text":"the experimenter would look at it,"},{"time":612237,"text":"scan it from top to bottom,"},{"time":613996,"text":"say \"Uh huh,\" and put it\non the pile next to them."},{"time":618680,"text":"In the second condition,\npeople did not write their name on it."},{"time":621990,"text":"The experimenter looked at it,"},{"time":624379,"text":"took the sheet of paper,\ndid not look at it, did not scan it,"},{"time":627346,"text":"and simply put it on the pile of pages."},{"time":630974,"text":"So you take a piece,\nyou just put it on the side."},{"time":633534,"text":"In the third condition,"},{"time":634883,"text":"the experimenter got the sheet of paper,"},{"time":637250,"text":"and put it directly into a shredder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639756,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":643177,"text":"What happened in those three conditions?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645994,"text":"In this plot I'm showing you\nat what pay rate people stopped."},{"time":650220,"text":"So low numbers mean\nthat people worked harder."},{"time":652826,"text":"They worked for much longer."},{"time":654952,"text":"In the acknowledged condition,"},{"time":656530,"text":"people worked all the way\ndown to 15 cents."},{"time":659654,"text":"At 15 cents per page,"},{"time":661295,"text":"they basically stopped these efforts."},{"time":663642,"text":"In the shredder condition, it was twice\nas much -- 30 cents per sheet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668153,"text":"And this is basically\nthe result we had before."},{"time":670416,"text":"You shred people's efforts, output --"},{"time":673804,"text":"you get them not to be as happy\nwith what they're doing."},{"time":676488,"text":"But I should point out, by the way,"},{"time":678216,"text":"that in the shredder condition,\npeople could have cheated."},{"time":680970,"text":"They could have done not so good work,"},{"time":682999,"text":"because they realized\npeople were just shredding it."},{"time":685522,"text":"So maybe the first sheet\nyou'd do good work,"},{"time":687633,"text":"but then you see nobody\nis really testing it,"},{"time":689792,"text":"so you would do more and more and more."},{"time":691729,"text":"So in fact, in the shredder condition,"},{"time":693593,"text":"people could have submitted more work\nand gotten more money,"},{"time":696451,"text":"and put less effort into it."},{"time":698471,"text":"But what about the ignored condition?"},{"time":700440,"text":"Would the ignored condition\nbe more like the acknowledged"},{"time":703194,"text":"or more like the shredder,\nor somewhere in the middle?"},{"time":706137,"text":"It turns out it was\nalmost like the shredder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709473,"text":"Now there's good news and bad news here."},{"time":712917,"text":"The bad news is that ignoring\nthe performance of people"},{"time":717004,"text":"is almost as bad as shredding\ntheir effort in front of their eyes."},{"time":721300,"text":"Ignoring gets you a whole way out there."},{"time":725213,"text":"The good news is that by simply looking\nat something that somebody has done,"},{"time":729546,"text":"scanning it and saying \"Uh huh,\""},{"time":731563,"text":"that seems to be quite sufficient"},{"time":733173,"text":"to dramatically improve\npeople's motivations."},{"time":736585,"text":"So the good news is that adding motivation"},{"time":739389,"text":"doesn't seem to be so difficult."},{"time":741912,"text":"The bad news is\nthat eliminating motivations"},{"time":744090,"text":"seems to be incredibly easy,"},{"time":745865,"text":"and if we don't think about it\ncarefully, we might overdo it."},{"time":749681,"text":"So this is all in terms\nof negative motivation,"},{"time":753116,"text":"or eliminating negative motivation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756426,"text":"The next part I want to show you\nis something about positive motivation."},{"time":760473,"text":"So there is a store\nin the U.S. called IKEA."},{"time":764970,"text":"And IKEA is a store\nwith kind of okay furniture"},{"time":769199,"text":"that takes a long time to assemble."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771667,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":773714,"text":"I don't know about you,"},{"time":774890,"text":"but every time I assemble one of those,"},{"time":776787,"text":"it takes me much longer,\nit's much more effortful,"},{"time":779152,"text":"it's much more confusing,\nI put things in the wrong way --"},{"time":783186,"text":"I can't say I enjoy those pieces."},{"time":786175,"text":"I can't say I enjoy the process."},{"time":789040,"text":"But when I finish it,"},{"time":790700,"text":"I seem to like those\nIKEA pieces of furniture"},{"time":792842,"text":"more than I like other ones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794718,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795798,"text":"And there's an old story about cake mixes."},{"time":799758,"text":"So when they started\ncake mixes in the '40s,"},{"time":803009,"text":"they would take this powder\nand they would put it in a box,"},{"time":806489,"text":"and they would ask housewives\nto basically pour it in,"},{"time":809554,"text":"stir some water in it,"},{"time":811300,"text":"mix it, put it in the oven,\nand -- voila -- you had cake."},{"time":815586,"text":"But it turns out they were very unpopular."},{"time":817639,"text":"People did not want them,"},{"time":819474,"text":"and they thought about\nall kinds of reasons for that."},{"time":822023,"text":"Maybe the taste was not good?"},{"time":823456,"text":"No, the taste was great."},{"time":824656,"text":"What they figured out was\nthat there was not enough effort involved."},{"time":829680,"text":"It was so easy that nobody\ncould serve cake to their guests"},{"time":833081,"text":"and say, \"Here is my cake.\""},{"time":835389,"text":"No, it was somebody else's cake,\nas if you bought it in the store."},{"time":838989,"text":"It didn't really feel like your own."},{"time":841574,"text":"So what did they do?"},{"time":843043,"text":"They took the eggs and the milk\nout of the powder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846313,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":848063,"text":"Now you had to break\nthe eggs and add them,"},{"time":851904,"text":"you had to measure the milk\nand add it, mixing it."},{"time":855084,"text":"Now it was your cake.\nNow everything was fine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857941,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":860329,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867904,"text":"Now, I think a little bit\nlike the IKEA effect,"},{"time":870157,"text":"by getting people to work harder,"},{"time":871809,"text":"they actually got them to love\nwhat they're doing"},{"time":874246,"text":"to a higher degree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":876150,"text":"So how do we look at this\nquestion experimentally?"},{"time":879046,"text":"We asked people to build some origami."},{"time":881223,"text":"We gave them instructions\non how to create origami,"},{"time":884000,"text":"and we gave them a sheet of paper."},{"time":885762,"text":"And these were all novices,"},{"time":887604,"text":"and they built something\nthat was really quite ugly --"},{"time":890182,"text":"nothing like a frog or a crane."},{"time":893086,"text":"But then we told them,\n\"Look, this origami really belongs to us."},{"time":896151,"text":"You worked for us, but I'll tell\nyou what, we'll sell it to you."},{"time":899199,"text":"How much do you want to pay for it?\""},{"time":901610,"text":"And we measured how much\nthey were willing to pay for it."},{"time":904310,"text":"And we had two types of people:"},{"time":906142,"text":"We had the people who built it,"},{"time":908110,"text":"and the people who did not build it,"},{"time":909913,"text":"and just looked at it\nas external observers."},{"time":913173,"text":"And what we found\nwas that the builders thought"},{"time":915428,"text":"that these were beautiful\npieces of origami --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":918080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":919366,"text":"and they were willing to pay\nfive times more for them"},{"time":921881,"text":"than the people who just\nevaluated them externally."},{"time":924890,"text":"Now you could say --\nif you were a builder,"},{"time":927942,"text":"do you think [you'd say],\n\"Oh, I love this origami,"},{"time":931134,"text":"but I know that nobody\nelse would love it?\""},{"time":934474,"text":"Or \"I love this origami,\nand everybody else will love it as well?\""},{"time":939892,"text":"Which one of those two is correct?"},{"time":942297,"text":"Turns out the builders\nnot only loved the origami more,"},{"time":945773,"text":"they thought that everybody\nwould see the world in their view."},{"time":949101,"text":"They thought everybody else\nwould love it more as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":952451,"text":"In the next version,\nwe tried to do the IKEA effect."},{"time":954913,"text":"We tried to make it more difficult."},{"time":957126,"text":"So for some people, we gave the same task."},{"time":959778,"text":"For some people, we made it harder\nby hiding the instructions."},{"time":964001,"text":"At the top of the sheet,\nwe had little diagrams"},{"time":966407,"text":"of how you fold origami."},{"time":968390,"text":"For some people, we just eliminated that."},{"time":971151,"text":"So now this was tougher."},{"time":972867,"text":"What happened?"},{"time":974048,"text":"Well in an objective way,"},{"time":976119,"text":"the origami now was uglier,\nit was more difficult."},{"time":980064,"text":"Now when we looked at the easy\norigami, we saw the same thing --"},{"time":983095,"text":"builders loved it more,\nevaluators loved it less."},{"time":986341,"text":"When you looked at the hard instructions,"},{"time":988524,"text":"the effect was larger."},{"time":991246,"text":"Why?"},{"time":992422,"text":"Because now the builders\nloved it even more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":995516,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":996746,"text":"They put all this extra effort into it."},{"time":999352,"text":"And evaluators?"},{"time":1001212,"text":"They loved it even less."},{"time":1002863,"text":"Because in reality, it was even uglier\nthan the first version."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006736,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1008101,"text":"Of course, this tells you something\nabout how we evaluate things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012835,"text":"Now think about kids."},{"time":1015216,"text":"Imagine I asked you, \"How much\nwould you sell your kids for?\""},{"time":1019748,"text":"Your memories and associations and so on."},{"time":1021780,"text":"Most people would say\nfor a lot, a lot of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1024443,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1025631,"text":"On good days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027039,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1028303,"text":"But imagine this was slightly different."},{"time":1030232,"text":"Imagine if you did not have your kids."},{"time":1032066,"text":"And one day you went to the park\nand you met some kids."},{"time":1034825,"text":"They were just like your kids,"},{"time":1036331,"text":"and you played with them for a few hours,"},{"time":1038373,"text":"and when you were about to leave,\nthe parents said, \"Hey, by the way,"},{"time":1041746,"text":"just before you leave,\nif you're interested, they're for sale.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1044753,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046883,"text":"How much would you pay for them now?"},{"time":1049803,"text":"Most people say not that much."},{"time":1052549,"text":"And this is because our kids\nare so valuable,"},{"time":1056743,"text":"not just because of who they are,"},{"time":1058897,"text":"but because of us,"},{"time":1060532,"text":"because they are so connected to us,"},{"time":1062716,"text":"and because of the time and connection."},{"time":1065311,"text":"By the way, if you think\nIKEA instructions are not good,"},{"time":1068242,"text":"what about the instructions that come\nwith kids, those are really tough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1071654,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072686,"text":"By the way, these are my kids, which,\nof course, are wonderful and so on."},{"time":1076952,"text":"Which comes to tell you one more thing,"},{"time":1078900,"text":"which is, much like our builders,"},{"time":1081374,"text":"when they look at the creature\nof their creation,"},{"time":1085239,"text":"we don't see that other people\ndon't see things our way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1090463,"text":"Let me say one last comment."},{"time":1093162,"text":"If you think about Adam Smith\nversus Karl Marx,"},{"time":1096979,"text":"Adam Smith had a very important\nnotion of efficiency."},{"time":1100750,"text":"He gave an example of a pin factory."},{"time":1103464,"text":"He said pins have 12 different steps,"},{"time":1106445,"text":"and if one person does all 12 steps,\nproduction is very low."},{"time":1110818,"text":"But if you get one person to do step one,"},{"time":1112970,"text":"and one person to do step two\nand step three and so on,"},{"time":1115747,"text":"production can increase tremendously."},{"time":1118382,"text":"And indeed, this is a great example,"},{"time":1120145,"text":"and the reason for the Industrial\nRevolution and efficiency."},{"time":1124270,"text":"Karl Marx, on the other hand,"},{"time":1125880,"text":"said that the alienation\nof labor is incredibly important"},{"time":1129365,"text":"in how people think about the connection\nto what they are doing."},{"time":1132785,"text":"And if you do all 12 steps,\nyou care about the pin."},{"time":1136079,"text":"But if you do one step every time,\nmaybe you don't care as much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1140568,"text":"I think that in the Industrial Revolution,"},{"time":1143377,"text":"Adam Smith was more\ncorrect than Karl Marx."},{"time":1146488,"text":"But the reality is that we've switched,"},{"time":1149347,"text":"and now we're in the knowledge economy."},{"time":1151379,"text":"You can ask yourself, what happens\nin a knowledge economy?"},{"time":1154290,"text":"Is efficiency still more\nimportant than meaning?"},{"time":1157561,"text":"I think the answer is no."},{"time":1158995,"text":"I think that as we move to situations"},{"time":1161213,"text":"in which people have\nto decide on their own"},{"time":1164196,"text":"about how much effort, attention,\ncaring, how connected they feel to it,"},{"time":1168390,"text":"are they thinking about labor\non the way to work,"},{"time":1170789,"text":"and in the shower and so on,"},{"time":1172390,"text":"all of a sudden Marx\nhas more things to say to us."},{"time":1176843,"text":"So when we think about labor,"},{"time":1178273,"text":"we usually think about motivation\nand payment as the same thing,"},{"time":1181697,"text":"but the reality is that we should\nprobably add all kinds of things to it --"},{"time":1185323,"text":"meaning, creation, challenges,\nownership, identity, pride, etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1189823,"text":"The good news is that if we added\nall of those components"},{"time":1192530,"text":"and thought about them --"},{"time":1194132,"text":"how do we create our own\nmeaning, pride, motivation,"},{"time":1197569,"text":"and how do we do it in our workplace,"},{"time":1199443,"text":"and for the employees --"},{"time":1200865,"text":"I think we could get people to be\nboth more productive and happier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1204854,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1206184,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}